{
  "id": "lotr_past_simple_dialogue",
  "title": "The Lord of the Rings: Past Simple",
  "description": "A dialogue about The Lord of the Rings focused on Past Simple practice.",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "id": "p_001",
      "text": "Did you watch The Lord of the Rings yesterday?",
      "ru": "Ты смотрел «Властелина колец» вчера?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-00.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_002",
      "text": "Yes, I watched the first part.",
      "ru": "Да, я посмотрел первую часть.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-00.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_003",
      "text": "Did you like the movie?",
      "ru": "Тебе понравился фильм?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-01.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_004",
      "text": "Yes, I liked it very much.",
      "ru": "Да, он мне очень понравился.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-01.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_005",
      "text": "What happened at the beginning of the movie?",
      "ru": "Что случилось в начале фильма?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-02.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_006",
      "text": "Bilbo gave the ring to Frodo.",
      "ru": "Бильбо дал кольцо Фродо.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-02.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_007",
      "text": "Did Frodo want to take the ring?",
      "ru": "Фродо хотел взять кольцо?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-03.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_008",
      "text": "No, he was afraid.",
      "ru": "Нет, он боялся.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-03.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_009",
      "text": "Did Gandalf help him?",
      "ru": "Гэндальф помог ему?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-04.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_010",
      "text": "Yes, Gandalf told him the truth.",
      "ru": "Да, Гэндальф рассказал ему правду.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-04.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_011",
      "text": "What did Frodo do then?",
      "ru": "Что Фродо сделал потом?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-05.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_012",
      "text": "He left the Shire with Sam.",
      "ru": "Он ушёл из Шира с Сэмом.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-05.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_013",
      "text": "Did they meet other hobbits?",
      "ru": "Они встретили других хоббитов?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-06.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_014",
      "text": "Yes, they met Merry and Pippin.",
      "ru": "Да, они встретили Мерри и Пиппина.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-06.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_015",
      "text": "Were they scared in the forest?",
      "ru": "Им было страшно в лесу?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-07.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_016",
      "text": "Yes, they saw dark riders.",
      "ru": "Да, они увидели тёмных всадников.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-07.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_017",
      "text": "Who saved them later?",
      "ru": "Кто спас их позже?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-08.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_018",
      "text": "Aragorn helped them at the inn.",
      "ru": "Арагорн помог им в трактире.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-08.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_019",
      "text": "Was he a strong warrior?",
      "ru": "Он был сильным воином?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-09.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_020",
      "text": "Yes, he fought well.",
      "ru": "Да, он хорошо сражался.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-09.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_021",
      "text": "Where did they go then?",
      "ru": "Куда они пошли потом?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-10.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_022",
      "text": "They went to Rivendell.",
      "ru": "Они пошли в Ривенделл.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-10.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_023",
      "text": "Was there a meeting there?",
      "ru": "Там было собрание?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-11.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_024",
      "text": "Yes, different peoples talked about the ring.",
      "ru": "Да, разные народы говорили о кольце.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-11.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_025",
      "text": "Who decided to destroy the ring?",
      "ru": "Кто решил уничтожить кольцо?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-12.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_026",
      "text": "Frodo decided to carry it to Mordor.",
      "ru": "Фродо решил нести его в Мордор.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-12.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_027",
      "text": "Did Sam go with him?",
      "ru": "Сэм пошёл с ним?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-13.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_028",
      "text": "Yes, Sam did not leave Frodo.",
      "ru": "Да, Сэм не оставил Фродо.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-13.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_029",
      "text": "Was the ending sad?",
      "ru": "Концовка была грустной?",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/question-14.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_030",
      "text": "Yes, but it was very powerful.",
      "ru": "Да, но она была очень сильной.",
      "audio": "audios/lotr_past_simple_dialogue/answer-14.mp3"
    }
  ]
}
